beer.beer_name: Brookvale Union: Spiced Rum Ginger Beer
beer.beer_description: Spicy yet mild, dry but wet, smooth but sharp, tight but loose. Just great tasting Ginger Beer with Spiced Rum & Lime!
The same ginger beer you know and love, with a little more oomph!  Full-flavoured refreshment in a can.

beer.beer_name: Brookvale Union: Boozy Seltzer - Juicy Juicy Grapefruit
beer.beer_description: Brookvale Union Boozy Seltzer Juicy Juicy Grapefruit contains less than 90 calories. Sweet yet citrusy, dry but juicy, sleek but spritzed, light but loose - just great tasting seltzer!

beer.beer_name: Brookvale Union: Citrusy Yuzu Ginger Beer
beer.beer_description: The same epic tasting ginger beer you know and love from Brookvale Union, with a citrusy yuzu twist. Hints of tangy citrus and real yuzu juice make this beverage incredibly sessionable for sunny days and balmy nights. Spicy yet mild, dry but wet, bitey but mellow, tight but loose  just great tasting flavoured ginger beer! Brookvale Union is all about quality nonsense. quality on the inside, nonsense on the outside and everywhere else.

The same epic tasting ginger beer you know and love from Brookvale Union, with a tropical twist. Hints of real mango and pineapple will have you singing sweet nothings and dancing in your floral skirt at first sip. Spicy yet mild, dry but wet, punchy but passion-y, tight but loose  just great tasting flavoured ginger beer!
